 the area:                             
 Use old toy factory as skill centre   
 Reduce vandalism                      
 Use more paint                        
 Tidy up the streets                   
 Parks for mothers and children        
 An adventure playground               
 Amusement centres                     
 Make roads smoother                   
 Another police station                
 Remove the abattoir:  it smells       
 Run express buses to Glasgow          
 Build a B.M.X. track                  
 No buses to park in main streets      
 Build an ice rink                     
 Renovate old houses                   
 Have more pals                        
 Less football in playground           
                                       
                                       
